
;=============================================
;Vars
;=============================================
;0: throw tech options
;1:
;2: Lightspeed Dash Meter (Max 300)
;3:
;4: Jump variable (from normal or super jump) - Ki Blast Charge Variable
;5: Allows player to use directions to change Pal (config)
;6:  System var. (OTG Juggling)
;7: System var. (for juggle limits)
;8: KO Voice choice
;9; Sonic Wind behind or in front
;10: Air dash limiter
;11: Spindash/Ring Burst/Dropdash Hitcount
;12: 5HP hitcount
;13: Super BG choice (config)
;14: Pursuit Limiter
;15: Animate blur through hitpause
;16: Homing Attack Limiter/Explod stuff
;The first 2 Bits are used to limit Homing Attack
;	1
;	2 - Homing Attack Limiter
;	4
;	8 - EX Homing Attack Limiter
;	16 - Cinematic Explod (HDBZ System)

;17: Zero Counter command
;18: JP
;19: 
;20: varset for 1st/2nd state of Focus Attack
;21: 
;22: Super jump var
;23: Focus Attack animelem set
;24: Focus Attack repel
;25: Sonic Wave speed
;26: Sonic Wind Level 2 On Block Hitcount
;27: First attack notification
;28: 
;29: 
;30: Dash Collision count - Beam Collision count
;31: Ticks Back is held down (Charge char)
;32: Back Charge Buffer (Charge char)
;33: Ticks Down is held down (Charge char)
;34: Down Charge Buffer (Charge char)
;35: Juggle Safety
;36: 
;37: superjump ai var (state 40)
;38: throw check
;39: Charge Time on En Homing Attack
;40: Ring SND Play for Electric Shield
;41: 
;42: Some More Bits
;  1 - Lightspeed Dash PalFX
;  2 - Turn Off Invuln Sonic Wind
;  4 - Speed Boost FX on or off
;  8 - Continue Stop Sound If no skip 
;  16 - Air Taunt Limiter
;  32 - Dropdash Limiter
;  64 - Has Speed Boost Afterimage played?
;  128 - Allow PalFX for Gem FX
;  256 - Turn on Lightning Shield
;  512 - Air H Lightspeed Cancel Bit
;  1024 - Ground H Lightspeed Cancel Bit
;  2048 - Ground L/M Lightspeed Cancel Bit
;  4096 - Turn On Typical HDBZ Chaining
;  8192 - Medium Tatsu Launch Limiter
;  16384 - Ring Burst Stop SND Bit
;  32768 - Loop Kick Hit Var
;  65536 - Turn on Finisher Music
;  131072 - Parry Emo Loss
;  262144 - Finisher Epilepsy Toggle
;  524288 - Did bro do the QTE
;  1048576 - Hit Bit for Air Trick
;  2097152 - Sonic Wind Hit Var
;  4194304 - Spindash Hit Bit
;  8388608 - EX Air Trick Attack Limiter
;  16777216 - LSD Input Check for Meter Dump Version
;  33554432 - Rings have been dropped
;  67108864 - Super Cancel Into Parry Attack
;  134217728 - L Air Trick Attack Limiter
;  268435456 - Air LSA Limiter
;  536870912 - 5LP Chain Limiter
;  1073741824 - 2LK Chain Limiter
;  

;43: Gem Status (Emo Exit)
; = 1 is Blue Gem
; = 2 is Green Gem
; = 3 is Yellow Gem
; = 4 is White Gem
; = 0 is off

;44: Repel Projectile choice (config)
;45: X axis Emo Gauge (config)
;46: Y axis Emo Gauge (config)
;47: flip knockout bounce
;48: AI Random Var
;49: Quickness Bar Meter Penalty
;50: Temp Var 
;51: EMOTION MODE - Activation variable (0 or 1)
;52: EMOTION MODE - Meter variable (Max 600)
;53: Extra/Cancel Bits
;  1 - Special Cancel
;  2 - Super Cancel
;  4 - Homing Attack Cancel
;  8 - Bit Check for Alt Transformation
;  16 - Double Jump Limiter
;  32 - Send P1 to Invisible State (Finisher)


;54: WINPOSE Bits
;  1 - Did Tails Appear?
;  2 - Did Shadow Appear?
;  4 - Check for Vegeta
;  8 - Check for Goku Black
;  16 - Check for Goku
;  32 - Check for Other Sonics
;  64 - Check for SSJ Charas
;  128 - Check for Broly
;  256 - Check for Self
;  512 - Check for Yoshin Broly
